{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Storage.removeItem()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/getItem\"><code>getItem()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/key\"><code>key()</code></a></li><li><em><code>removeItem()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/setItem\"><code>setItem()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Storage API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage\"><code>Window.localStorage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage\"><code>Window.sessionStorage</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die Methode <code>removeItem()</code> der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a>-Schnittstelle löscht den im Parameter keyName benannten Datensatz aus dem Speicher. Ist kein Datensatz unter diesem Schlüssel vorhanden, tut diese Funktion nichts.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>storage</em>.removeItem(<em>keyName</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"keyname\"><em><u>keyName</u></em></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>, der den Schlüssel des zu löschenden Datensatzes enthält.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Keiner.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die nachfolgende Funktion speichert drei Datensätze und löscht abschließend den Datensatz mit dem Schlüssel <code>image</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">populateStorage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'bgcolor'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'font'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Helvetica'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'myCat.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  localStorage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeItem</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Weitere Beispiele sind im <a href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/web-storage/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web-Storage-Demo</a> zu finden.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webstorage.html#dom-storage-removeitem\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Storage.removeItem' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.Storage.removeItem","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API/Using_the_Web_Storage_API\">Using the Web Storage API</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Methode removeItem() der Storage-Schnittstelle löscht den im Parameter keyName benannten Datensatz aus dem Speicher. Ist kein Datensatz unter diesem Schlüssel vorhanden, tut diese Funktion nichts.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Storage.removeItem()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/storage/removeitem","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/storage/removeitem/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage","title":"Storage"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Storage/removeItem","title":"Storage.removeItem()"}],"pageTitle":"Storage.removeItem() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}